Package: rlaqn
Title: Data retrieval from the London Air API
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Justin", "Lingard", email = "prejjnl@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: rlaqn allows retrieval of data from the London Air API, the data feed of the London Air Quality Network, operated by the Environemntal Research Group (ERG) at King's College London (KCL). The API provides a structured and convenient way to interact with the data from the LAQN. Data is supplied in JSON format.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
License: 
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
